With Blendtec jars, you won’t waste time tending your blends with a tamper to get all the ingredients down into the blades, and no tamper means one less thing to clean when you’re done.Blendtec blenders can also heat your food during the blend cycle. The time it takes to make each course could be measured in seconds not minutes or hours.
